{"tid":2076863,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Draymond Green :希望有一天Lebron James可以出來選總統","createTime":"2020-06-24T01:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T11:11:29.000Z","uid":150100,"like":5,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a397ee744576c7298e8c1e0fc83f97056da37e59","tid":2076863,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T01:00:07.000Z","msg":"「LeBron可以說是史上最偉大的球員，看看他的生涯成就，那真的是無可挑剔，不論是球場上或球場外都是。球場上，他擁有輝煌的成就，但我認為更重要的是球場外的部份，而這也是我為何如此尊敬他。」<br />\n<br />\n「身為他在球場上的競爭對手，我非常享受和他打球，但他在場外的成就顯示了他同時也是一位傑出的領袖。希望有一天他可以出來選總統。」<br />\n<br />\n-Draymond Green談論LeBron James的影響力<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/181465895202703/posts/3599761553373103/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F181465895202703%2Fposts%2F3599761553373103%2F&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=2430960a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/181465895202703/posts/3599761553373103/</a><br />\n<br />\n原來唔只我一個咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望勒邦占士退休之後會去選美國總統<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1794288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1794288</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n希望Lebron James 退休選美國總統<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1977883\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1977883</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n希望勒邦占士退休之後可以競選美國總統<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2050507\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2050507</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"028c719a06b1a7c10a3a727fc28f4ecfe6a9140a","tid":2076863,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T01:02:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">THE KING！！！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6c8127865010730d9ba97c13568b65f215683d72","tid":2076863,"uid":322032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T01:04:48.000Z